description:
At this point in our lives... there is no space for indifference. If you realize that Twitter started labeling the tweets from the PRESIDENT of the USA as misleading...then you have to ask yourself a couple of things. First of all who gave twitter the authority of the truth? Second why would they do that? Third who will benefit from this the most? Fourth do I believe in democracy? Fifth where the hell is our freedom of speech then? I don’t really care if you’re left or right .... I care if you’re for humanity. Although you might think well what do I have to lose or it doesn’t impact me ... then ask yourself the question ... if even the most powerful person in the USA get’s silenced... what does that mean for me?  Does my voice matter? My rights? My freedom? My future? Don’t you wonder what the real purpose is of all the social media channels we have? Think about that... before it’s too late...and the West turns into China 🙏🏻 ⁣
